data.description: Great curb appeal greets you when you come to see this charming Diego with 2 bedrooms plus an extra room which could be an office, den, hobby room or easily converted into a third bedroom if needed.  Both bathrooms in the home have lovely granite counter tops and the Primary Bedroom has a walk-in closet.  The Kitchen features all stainless steel appliances plus a spacious breakfast nook with bay window and opens to the family room with sliding glass door out to the large full-length covered patio in your private backyard.  The HVAC was replaced 3 years ago with a new energy efficient system to save you money on your heating and AC costs.  Don't miss this opportunity to enjoy the great SaddleBrooke lifestyle today!
